title: DAKINE Drafter Pack
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2011 Drafter Pack, shown in Phantom camo print.

Pack Features
- 100oz / 3L reservoir with Quick Disconnect hose
- Molded back panel with Air Channel Ventilation
- Full face or XC helmet carry
- Armor carry straps
- Padded MP3
